      "content": "hey, i keep getting a MemoryError when trying to process some massive csv files in my pandas script. i'm currently using a list comprehension to pull certain columns, but it seems to be eating up all my ram. would using a generator instead of a list comprehension help with the memory footprint, or is there a better way to handle this? thanks",
